Name: Sedition of Imbibitor Lunae (I)
Desc: When an ally uses their Ultimate, obtain Memory Imprint. This effect stacks up to <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak></color> time(s). At the start of every Cycle, regenerate Energy to all allies based on the number of Memory Imprint stacks (Each stack regenerates <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#3[i]</unbreak></color> Energy). Energy obtained in this way can exceed allies' Max Energy.

Challenge.Name: Win with at least <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> Cycle(s) left
Win with at least <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> Cycle(s) left
Have no downed characters
